7–8. Karacaraṇamudujālatālakkhaṇāni ^n210 “Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato purimaṁ jātiṁ purimaṁ bhavaṁ purimaṁ niketaṁ pubbe manussabhūto samāno 
