9–10. Ussaṅkhapāda-uddhaggalomatālakkhaṇāni ^n212 “Yampi, bhikkhave, tathāgato purimaṁ jātiṁ purimaṁ bhavaṁ purimaṁ niketaṁ pubbe manussabhūto samāno 
