Tena so sucaritena kammunā, 
Suggatiṁ vajati tattha modati; 
Lakkhaṇāni ca duve idhāgato, 
Uttamappamukhatāya vindati. 
Ubbhamuppatitalomavā saso, 
Pādagaṇṭhirahu sādhusaṇṭhitā; 
