Uparicaraṇasobhanā ahu. 
Gehamāvasati ce tathāvidho, 
Aggataṁ vajati kāmabhoginaṁ; 
Tena uttaritaro na vijjati, 
Jambudīpamabhibhuyya iriyati. 
Pabbajampi ca anomanikkamo, 
